cf.DimensionCoordinate.valid_max¶

DimensionCoordinate.valid_max¶

The valid_max CF property.

Examples: 
>>> f.valid_max = 100.0
>>> f.valid_max
100.0
>>> del f.valid_max

>>> f.setprop('valid_max', 100.0)
>>> f.getprop('valid_max')
100.0
>>> f.delprop('valid_max')
